 7068 . Many in the United States are worried by the lack of freedom and human rights in China .
 During the Tiananmen Square massacre in Beijing on June 4 , 1989 , thousands of pro - democracy protestors were arrested and many were killed as Chinese authorities fired into the crowd and tanks crushed people who attempted to wall them out .
 Over one thousand more dissidents were arrested in the following weeks as the Chinese government investigated the planning of the protests in the square .
